              representative of our community. You gain the power to voice your ideas, shape our creative direction, and fundamentally influence
              everything we do. In essence, you become the boss, and we work for you. Your insights will directly inform which projects receive priority
              and where our resources and funding are strategically allocated.
            </p>

            <p>
              The funding you provide is the lifeblood of Majestic Media, granting us the creative freedom to develop the shows you are
              passionate about. It allows us to invest more time into production and acquire additional talent, enabling us to deliver an ever-expanding
              volume of high-quality content. Together, we can ensure Majestic Media's continued expansion and growth.
            </p>

            <h2>Exclusive Curator Privileges</h2>
            <p>As a Majestic Media curator, you unlock a suite of exclusive benefits designed to give you unparalleled influence and access:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Project Greenlighting Authority:</strong> Cast your vote on all proposed projects, directly deciding which shows receive the green light for production.</li>
              <li><strong>"Chrono-Viewer" Database Influence:</strong> Gain the ability to actively add and modify data within the "Chrono-Viewer" database, contributing directly to our content foundation.</li>
              <li><strong>Participating Critic Role:</strong> Engage as an official critic in shows such as "Forgotten Media," providing your expert insights.</li>
              <li><strong>Priority Access for Submissions:</strong> Your nominations, submissions, comments, and questions will receive front-of-the-line prioritization for shows including "The Stories We Tell," "Modern Tall Tales," "Hidden Talents," and "The Bok Project."</li>
              <li><strong>Exclusive Character Naming Opportunity:</strong> Early curators will be granted the unique honor of naming a character within the "Simulated" series.</li>
              <li><strong>"Unscripted" Studio Audience:</strong> Become part of the studio audience for shows like "Unscripted," experiencing the production process firsthand.</li>
              <li><strong>"Jackbox Party" Competition:</strong> Participate in our exclusive, interactive "Jackbox Party" game show competitions.</li>
              <li><strong>Discounted Media Access:</strong> Receive all four books in "The Order of Chaos" novel series, a copy of "The Dire Realm" Card Game, and the "Interstellar" Mobile Game at a 30% discount upon their public release.</li>
              <li><strong>Direct Project Pitching:</strong> Present your own original show concepts for consideration and potential development by Majestic Media.</li>
