        <section id="tab-producer" class="tab-panel" aria-hidden="true" style="display:none;"> <header class="sp-header">  <h2>Opportunity: Join Majestic Media as a Contributing Producer</h2> </header> <div class="sp-body" aria-live="polite"> <p> As the Executive Producer of Majestic Media, I am expanding our team to enhance our capacity and accelerate project completion. With numerous ambitious projects underway, I recognize the need for talented individuals to contribute their expertise. If you resonate with our content and possess a background that aligns with any of our initiatives, I invite you to consider a unique and equitable collaboration. </p>
<h3>Our Compensation Model</h3>
<p>
  At Majestic Media, we are committed to a compensation model that directly rewards individual contribution and incentivizes
  high-quality, efficient work. We believe in shared success: as the projects you contribute to thrive, so too should your earnings.
  Our compensation structure is designed for transparency and direct correlation to project success:
</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Monthly Performance Review:</strong> Once a month, I will conduct a comprehensive financial review. This will involve analyzing YouTube analytics for each project's content, compiling revenue from our curator community, and calculating contributions from sponsors. This sum represents the total revenue generated by each project.</li>
  <li><strong>Project Assignment:</strong> As a producer, you will have the autonomy to select the project you are most passionate about contributing to. The total revenue attributed to your chosen project will directly reflect the financial impact of your work within Majestic Media.</li>
  <li><strong>Revenue Allocation:</strong> Fifty percent (50%) of the project's gross revenue will be allocated to cover operational costs and reinvestment into future project development. The remaining fifty percent (50%) will be deposited into a dedicated "shares" account.</li>
  <li><strong>Share Distribution:</strong> As a contributing producer, you will hold one (1) share in this account. As the Executive Producer, I will also hold one (1) share. For instance, if a project generates $10,000 in a given month and involves two total shares, your monthly compensation would be $5,000.</li>
</ul>

<p>
  This model directly links your compensation to productivity and project success. Should the project require additional support, necessitating the onboarding of another producer, their share would be factored into the distribution. However, the increased output and potential for higher revenue generated by an expanded team are expected to proportionally increase the overall pool for distribution, maintaining a balanced outcome.
</p>

<p>
  We offer flexible payment schedules (monthly, bi-weekly, or weekly) to accommodate your preferences. Your contribution is integral to Majestic Media's success, and we are committed to ensuring you receive a fair share of the profits you help generate. Does this compensation structure align with your professional aspirations?
</p>

<h3>Requirements for Collaboration</h3>
<p>To be considered for a contributing producer role, please provide:</p>
<ul>
  <li>A comprehensive resume or a link to your LinkedIn profile, showcasing your relevant professional background.</li>
  <li>Samples of your previous work, if available, demonstrating your capabilities.</li>
  <li>Necessary tax information documentation. Please note that this position will likely be structured as a 1099 contractor role.</li>
  <li>All requisite equipment and a reliable internet connection to perform your duties remotely. For example, video editors will need their own professional editing workstations.</li>
</ul>

<p>
  Majestic Media embraces a remote-first work environment. Your physical location is not a barrier to collaboration. Assignments will be delivered digitally, and you will be granted online access to all necessary materials, enabling you to produce and transfer content seamlessly. The majority of these positions do not require a physical presence. We welcome applications from qualified individuals globally.
</p>

<h3>Open Positions</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Producer/Editor: "Chrono-Viewer: Media Edition" and "Chrono-Viewer: History Edition"</li>
  <li>Producer/Editor/Blender Artist: "Forgotten Media"</li>
  <li>Producer/Editor/Journalist/Interviewer: "The Stories We Tell" and "Modern Tall Tales"</li>
  <li>Producer/Director/Editor/Writer: "Unscripted" (Preferably based in or near the Milwaukee metropolitan area for logistical reasons)</li>
  <li>Comedians: "Unscripted"</li>
  <li>Game Developer: "Probe: A Space Exploration Game"</li>
  <li>Business Manager: "School of Media"</li>
  <li>Business Manager: “Majestic Media” (I’m a creative mind. I would be happy to turn over the running of the company to someone else so I can focus on the creative side of things.)</li>
</ul>

<p>To apply, please use the contact box below. All submissions are sent to <a href="mailto:connect@majesticmediastudios.com">connect@majesticmediastudios.com</a></p>

